    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 3.5288002491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！　これが今日のライブの合間にやる、伊吹渚\nプレゼンツ、『胸キュン告白選手権Z』の台本だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8000000725,
      "endTime": 12.881088901600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 5.3000001599
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0768030573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ゼットって何……？\n最終形態っていうこと？　よく分かんないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0768030573,
      "endTime": 19.6810895373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8768036931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "胸キュン告白選手権というと、サニピもやっていた\n渚ちゃんの台本を元に告白の実演をする企画でしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8768036931,
      "endTime": 28.7965537161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9922678719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。ずっと要望もあったからね。今回はさらに改良\nして、なんと私が胸キュンコメンテーターを務めます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9922678719,
      "endTime": 38.1922674905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3879816462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "胸キュン……コメンテーター？\nそれってどんなことするの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3879816462,
      "endTime": 44.5295234133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7252375692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "みんながそれぞれ告白した後に\n私の独断と偏見で、告白の感想を言おうと思うんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7252375692,
      "endTime": 52.117391595200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3131057511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "告白した後いじられるってこと！？\nそれ渚が感想を言いたいだけな気がするんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3131057511,
      "endTime": 58.5268244515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7131057511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でもでも面白そう！\n月ストにもやってほしいって前から言われてたもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7131057511,
      "endTime": 64.4975503693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6932645251
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私には難しいかもしれませんが……\nバレンタインにふさわしい企画だとは、思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6932645251,
      "endTime": 72.5938943317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.7896084875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "伊吹渚プロが今日のために考えてきたんですもの\nファンの要望もありますし、無下には出来ませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7896084875,
      "endTime": 83.0597899526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな乗り気なんだ\nうぅ、恥ずかしいけど……分かった、私もやるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2562751542,
      "endTime": 93.4362752687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 86.3608903308
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6229418208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、みんな！\nきっとファンの人達も喜んで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6229418208,
      "endTime": 97.8989962031,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4371.767012300012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3666622887
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 97.9947088331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと待ちなさい。よく見たら\n私の内容だけ渚に向けての告白じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9947088331,
      "endTime": 103.334708795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5280421664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "バ、バレた……あはは……\nちゃんとファンに向けたものも準備してるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5280421664,
      "endTime": 111.3985635211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 111.594277677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "油断も隙もないんだから、まったく……\nでも、渚はセンターになっても渚のままね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.594277677,
      "endTime": 119.9374295324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1276110103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それがね……実は結構緊張してて……\n油断したら足が、子鹿みたいになっちゃうくらいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1276110103,
      "endTime": 131.593121188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 131.7888353438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、一度気合いを入れた方がいいかもね\nいつものやりましょうか。渚は私と、場所交代ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7888353438,
      "endTime": 140.8591524214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 141.0555020105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0555020105,
      "endTime": 142.3931890737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 142.5889032295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫\n今度は、私が照らすから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5889032295,
      "endTime": 146.8750856808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0888950915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、歌いましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
